data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat with easy access to outdoor adventures with a boat launch just 3 minutes away.! This expansive abode boasts stunning views of the tranquil lake and majestic Owyhee Mountains.  The property features lush landscaping, orchard with automatic sprinklers, and a cozy fireplace for chilly evenings. Bask in natural light or enjoy the pellet stove in the enclosed sunroom compete w/ hand-laid Saltillo tiles. The master bedroom offers a private balcony overlooking the scenery. Modern comforts abound with newer appliances, gas heat, and a gas on-demand water heater. Stay toasty with two pellet stoves and relish ample storage in the chef's kitchen with an industrial cooktop. Outdoor entertaining is a breeze on the covered deck with an outdoor kitchen. Additional highlights include a loafing shed, tack room, and a shop with 220v power and boat storage. Discover the perfect blend of luxury and convenience with this idyllic property, complete with a cold room. This home has a 2.25% assum loan!
